{"tid":295342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺兩個人出街對方係咁㩒手機，真係好唔尊重","createTime":"2017-06-23T16:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T23:10:06.000Z","uid":17124,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b02fe8c447863ee4b19635b9c32fa649807ecad2","tid":295342,"uid":17124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:21:38.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得同人單獨出街/食飯，對方係咁㩒手機，真係好唔尊重。<br />\n特別係當你係咁嘗試帶起話題，對方回應幾句就算繼續自己㩒手機，完全唔會試下帶起另一個話題，真係會覺得好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔想再同佢講野。<br />\n重點係你講佢日常生活興趣既野就肯同你傾下，到你分享翻自己野就一句 哦 咁就算，成段對話完全唔係雙向。<br />\n朋友係咁都話可以疏遠，女朋友係咁就真係唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n覺得好辛苦，雖然話會改但都係唔覺有咩改變，佢攰時我又攰，咁唔通大家就唔洗溝通？"},{"pid":"099fc4d7eb72ff521cd3d8e77b59c3d8263d0daa","tid":295342,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:37:20.000Z","msg":"覺呀，對朋友我會直接講出來<br />\n未有女朋友，但好似真係講唔出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c30b709729cd43007d36eb5030b8cc973c98184","tid":295342,"uid":17124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺呀，對朋友我會直接講出來<br />\n未有女朋友，但好似真係講唔出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經因為依樣野同佢嗌過幾次交，佢話攰唔想講野，但其實咁都會搞到我好攰好灰<br />\n點解你想傾嗰陣我就要陪你傾，相反就要我遷就你，成件事根本唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dd527648bbeaf7047bdac120b23c01b6dec1b8","tid":295342,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"覺得你悶咪禁電話<br />\n<br />\n唔改善既似下實俾帽你認真<br />\n<br />\n女人好愛新鮮感"},{"pid":"c2c059616b27843e0ffd91136d410bb11ee566f0","tid":295342,"uid":17124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得你悶咪禁電話<br />\n<br />\n唔改善既似下實俾帽你認真<br />\n<br />\n女人好愛新鮮感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有可能係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之前話過冇野講先㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4b4122122d8852bcec72e29619aee422acf086","tid":295342,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得你悶咪禁電話<br />\n<br />\n唔改善既似下實俾帽你認真<br />\n<br />\n女人好愛新鮮感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有可能係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之前話過冇野講先㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋幾耐見一次？"},{"pid":"3732ccd6fa4fae34c02d1d586483a25b736c8115","tid":295342,"uid":17124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得你悶咪禁電話<br />\n<br />\n唔改善既似下實俾帽你認真<br />\n<br />\n女人好愛新鮮感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有可能係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之前話過冇野講先㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋幾耐見一次？</blockquote><br />\n日日都見，但依個問題持續左好耐<br />\n因為以前我都仲有心機引佢講野，但依家覺得不停做主動真係好攰"},{"pid":"13da9f464d72f77e7b91a20ab682f09ebbcdf6c0","tid":295342,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T22:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得你悶咪禁電話<br />\n<br />\n唔改善既似下實俾帽你認真<br />\n<br />\n女人好愛新鮮感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有可能係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之前話過冇野講先㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋幾耐見一次？</blockquote><br />\n日日都見，但依個問題持續左好耐<br />\n因為以前我都仲有心機引佢講野，但依家覺得不停做主動真係好攰</blockquote><br />\n分手吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁唔開心"},{"pid":"fec08c09e0afabc265eebc86e89eac0fab62f106","tid":295342,"uid":91233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>覺得你悶咪禁電話<br />\n<br />\n唔改善既似下實俾帽你認真<br />\n<br />\n女人好愛新鮮感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有可能係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢之前話過冇野講先㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你哋幾耐見一次？</blockquote><br />\n日日都見，但依個問題持續左好耐<br />\n因為以前我都仲有心機引佢講野，但依家覺得不停做主動真係好攰</blockquote><br />\n日日見其實有無咁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講野咪拖住佢行下街 應該唔會尷尬<br />\n利申：A0"},{"pid":"fae7c0ccfd92deae849252625ddfda43c48417d6","tid":295342,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T23:10:06.000Z","msg":"我條女掉返轉唔準我㩒<br />\n就算覆公司嘢都黑面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}